// EFFECTIVE UNTIL JUNE 30, 2015 PER CHAPTERS 280 AND 281 OF 2011 //
To apply for a registration, an applicant shall submit to the Commissioner an application on the form that the Commissioner provides.
The application shall include:
The applicant's legal name, trade name, if any, main office address, telephone number, electronic mail address, if any, and Web site address, if any;
The name, address, and telephone number of the applicant's designated contact for receipt of complaints;
The name, address, and telephone number of the applicant's resident agent in the State; and
Any other information that the Commissioner reasonably requires.
